Week 4 Part A - AgenticAI and Application Project Submission
The Project has 4 files/code cells
1. Class Book
2. Class Library
3. Main.py
4. books.csv

The main program runs in a loop until quit by user and has 5 options provided
0. Load books from csv file
1. Add a book
2. Display books
3. Borrow a book
4. Return a book
5. Exit

The Library class uses a simple list to store Books (Type Class Book)
Borrowing a book, uses search book by author or title functions to find and return the book. 
Then based on availability it will borrow the successfully and updates the availability flag as "Issued". 
If the book is already "Issues" then it return the message book cannot be borrowed. 

The Book class uses Itertool function count and next to create unique indexes for each book

Limitations/ToDo:
The search functions needs to be refined further to use ignorecase options to compare auther and titles.
